&lt;li&gt;Lead and support strategy development and implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead quantitative and qualitative analysis for growth strategies and operational improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide actionable strategy recommendations based on your analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as an active thought partner for all areas of the business, incl. GTM, product and engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present and discuss findings with senior management and board members (C-suite, Thoma Bravo) in close collaboration with operating leaders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the strategic evaluation of M&amp;amp;A opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
