&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in an analytic discipline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum two years of experience at a top-tier strategy consulting firm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience serving clients in SaaS or private equity a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to drive both quantitative and qualitative workstreams independently, incl. ability to workplan&lt;/li&gt;
